00:32:59.510 --> 00:33:02.030
LUVVIE AJAYI: The thing
is that we've been told,

00:33:02.030 --> 00:33:04.740
we've been too everything
for a long time--

00:33:04.740 --> 00:33:08.840
too sensitive, too much,
too loud, too bossy,

00:33:08.840 --> 00:33:10.940
too assertive, right?

00:33:10.940 --> 00:33:14.030
So we've erred on the
other side in order

00:33:14.030 --> 00:33:16.190
to make sure we're not too.

00:33:16.190 --> 00:33:19.200
You will always be
too to somebody.

00:33:19.200 --> 00:33:20.670
No matter who you are.

00:33:20.670 --> 00:33:27.050
You will always be too much, too
loud, too quiet, too sensitive,

00:33:27.050 --> 00:33:28.430
to somebody.

00:33:28.430 --> 00:33:31.130
In those moments, honestly,
just do a gut check.

00:33:31.130 --> 00:33:32.690
How am I feeling right now?

00:33:32.690 --> 00:33:38.290
Does this actually feel like
something that is not OK?

00:33:38.290 --> 00:33:40.090
That is the only
question to ask yourself.

00:33:40.090 --> 00:33:44.630
If the answer is yes,
it does not feel OK.

00:33:44.630 --> 00:33:46.762
Don't ask yourself 15 questions.

00:33:46.762 --> 00:33:49.220
Because you will always talk
yourself out of those moments.

00:33:49.220 --> 00:33:50.960
You will always talk
yourself out of speaking out.

00:33:50.960 --> 00:33:52.543
Because you'll be
like, you know what?

00:33:52.543 --> 00:33:55.370
I'm not going to be
any type of trouble

00:33:55.370 --> 00:33:57.380
because I don't want
to be too something.

00:33:57.380 --> 00:33:58.410
Listen.

00:33:58.410 --> 00:33:59.960
Get used to being too something.

00:33:59.960 --> 00:34:00.620
[LAUGHTER]

00:34:00.620 --> 00:34:03.410
You will always be too
something to somebody.

00:34:03.410 --> 00:34:06.110
There are moments where you can
even make yourself more quiet,

00:34:06.110 --> 00:34:08.510
and even somebody will
still find you too loud.

00:34:08.510 --> 00:34:09.260
And you know what?

00:34:09.260 --> 00:34:10.580
Next time I need to
give you something

00:34:10.580 --> 00:34:12.955
to make you feel like I was
too loud, for real, for real.

00:34:12.955 --> 00:34:14.420
[LAUGHTER]

00:34:14.420 --> 00:34:18.139
So I mean, I have to
say you have to do a gut

00:34:18.139 --> 00:34:19.760
check with yourself.

00:34:19.760 --> 00:34:25.110
And just figure out
did that feel good?

00:34:25.110 --> 00:34:26.670
That is really the question.

00:34:26.670 --> 00:34:27.449
Did it feel good?

00:34:27.449 --> 00:34:30.530
If it did not feel good,
then that joke was not OK.

00:34:30.530 --> 00:34:33.650
And also, if the
joke is making me

00:34:33.650 --> 00:34:37.460
feel like less than a
person, or if the joke makes

00:34:37.460 --> 00:34:42.139
me feel like my voice does not
matter, that's a terrible joke.

00:34:42.139 --> 00:34:45.590
If the joke makes me
feel like I'm not safe,

00:34:45.590 --> 00:34:47.239
that's a terrible joke.

00:34:47.239 --> 00:34:50.520
So whoever is making
it, a boy or a girl,

00:34:50.520 --> 00:34:53.179
that's a terrible joke.

00:34:53.179 --> 00:34:54.060
And here's the thing.

00:34:54.060 --> 00:34:56.909
Here's a key you
can use if somebody

00:34:56.909 --> 00:34:59.550
