00:34:59.550 --> 00:35:01.020
that makes you
feel uncomfortable.

00:35:01.020 --> 00:35:02.470
Where you're, like, I
want to say something.

00:35:02.470 --> 00:35:03.600
I don't know what to say.

00:35:03.600 --> 00:35:05.780
Ask him a question.

00:35:05.780 --> 00:35:07.460
So say they make this joke.

00:35:07.460 --> 00:35:09.410
And they're, like, ha, right?

00:35:09.410 --> 00:35:10.930
You should be, like,
I don't get it.

00:35:10.930 --> 00:35:11.440
Explain that.

00:35:11.440 --> 00:35:12.273
What does that mean?

00:35:12.273 --> 00:35:12.820
[LAUGHTER]

00:35:12.820 --> 00:35:14.740
Literally, just ask
them the question.

00:35:14.740 --> 00:35:16.660
Because then, in that
moment, they actually

00:35:16.660 --> 00:35:19.360
have to explain
that joke to you.

00:35:19.360 --> 00:35:22.210
And if it's a
racist, homophobic--

00:35:22.210 --> 00:35:24.670
