is not appropriate,

00:35:24.670 --> 00:35:27.250
that person in that moment
is now put on the spot.

00:35:27.250 --> 00:35:28.580
Explain that.

00:35:28.580 --> 00:35:29.540
What does that mean?

00:35:29.540 --> 00:35:30.610
I don't get it.

00:35:30.610 --> 00:35:33.283
And then they'll have to
be, like, you know how.

00:35:33.283 --> 00:35:33.950
I know how what?

00:35:33.950 --> 00:35:35.660
[LAUGHTER]

00:35:35.660 --> 00:35:36.160
No.

00:35:36.160 --> 00:35:37.368
Ask questions.

00:35:37.368 --> 00:35:39.160
In fact, if you want
to challenge something

00:35:39.160 --> 00:35:41.080
that happens in a
room, and you don't

00:35:41.080 --> 00:35:45.230
