00:40:51.717 --> 00:40:53.560
like this shouldn't
happen like this.

00:40:53.560 --> 00:40:56.770
But they either lived
in a working environment

00:40:56.770 --> 00:41:00.490
where being challenged gets
you punished, which is awful,

00:41:00.490 --> 00:41:02.183
and that comes from
leadership down--

00:41:02.183 --> 00:41:03.850
if leadership has
created an environment

00:41:03.850 --> 00:41:07.780
where they are untouchable,
can't be challenged.

00:41:07.780 --> 00:41:09.280
If you listened to
the Theranos doc,

00:41:09.280 --> 00:41:11.350
you'll see that thing is real.

00:41:11.350 --> 00:41:14.500
People will end up just
not doing their best work

00:41:14.500 --> 00:41:18.280
because you never grow
from being challenged.

00:41:18.280 --> 00:41:21.010
Either that, or this person
who is sitting in the room

00:41:21.010 --> 00:41:22.670
was just like, this
is not my business.

00:41:22.670 --> 00:41:24.400
This is not my charge.

00:41:24.400 --> 00:41:26.260
So I'm not going to
speak up about it.

00:41:26.260 --> 00:41:27.937
Or this person was,
like, you know what?

00:41:27.937 --> 00:41:29.770
I'm usually the one
speaking up all the time

00:41:29.770 --> 00:41:31.052
being on the island by myself.

00:41:31.052 --> 00:41:33.260
Today I'm going to take a
