00:42:32.910 --> 00:42:34.380
been thought through.

00:42:34.380 --> 00:42:36.600
I have figured out
all the blind spots.

00:42:36.600 --> 00:42:39.600
I have figured out how
to make it already good

00:42:39.600 --> 00:42:43.440
so nobody in that room has
cause to challenge me on it.

00:42:43.440 --> 00:42:45.640
It will make you
step up your game.

00:42:45.640 --> 00:42:47.160
I know it makes me
