00:43:14.340 --> 00:43:15.590
You didn't think this through.

00:43:15.590 --> 00:43:17.050
Why are you wasting my time?

00:43:17.050 --> 00:43:19.390
It just makes everybody's
life better, easier,

00:43:19.390 --> 00:43:20.830
and you will do better work.

00:43:20.830 --> 00:43:22.610
NOEILA FENANDEZ ARROYO: Awesome.

00:43:22.610 --> 00:43:24.420
AUDIENCE: I have a
question about the fact

00:43:24.420 --> 00:43:28.230
