00:50:12.120 --> 00:50:13.895
I go to my board of directors.

00:50:13.895 --> 00:50:15.020
And they'll be, like, yeah.

00:50:15.020 --> 00:50:15.970
You did misstep there.

00:50:15.970 --> 00:50:16.760
And I'll be, like, OK.

00:50:16.760 --> 00:50:18.177
If you said that
to me, and you're

00:50:18.177 --> 00:50:19.700
someone who loves
me, who's smart,

00:50:19.700 --> 00:50:22.820
who's thoughtful about the
world, I will believe that.

00:50:22.820 --> 00:50:26.020
This doesn't mean you take
on every troll on Twitter.

00:50:26.020 --> 00:50:26.720
Because no.

00:50:26.720 --> 00:50:29.210
In fact, take on zero
trolls on Twitter.

00:50:29.210 --> 00:50:32.030
But also listen to the actual
constructive criticism.

00:50:32.030 --> 00:50:39.380
So a poem where a
white man is attempting

00:50:39.380 --> 00:50:42.890
to speak like
somebody who he has

00:50:42.890 --> 00:50:48.350
