00:50:52.460 --> 00:50:56.390
which is you shouldn't
make fun of people

00:50:56.390 --> 00:51:02.210
who are more marginalized
than you, essentially.

00:51:02.210 --> 00:51:05.870
Which is why black folks can
make fun of white people,

00:51:05.870 --> 00:51:07.480
because we're punching up.

