But they can absolutely
make fun of me.

00:51:18.520 --> 00:51:20.690
I can't make fun of them
for their trans identity.

00:51:20.690 --> 00:51:23.210
I can make fun of
other things, right?

00:51:23.210 --> 00:51:25.070
Because maybe they're
Scientologists.

00:51:25.070 --> 00:51:25.600
[LAUGHTER]

00:51:25.600 --> 00:51:28.870
But I'm terrible.

